{"tid":1248133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"包圍警總的各位冷靜","createTime":"2019-06-21T11:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T12:16:52.000Z","uid":265019,"like":23,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"ea3ff73bfffded7539ef0f5f3343c82333773390","tid":1248133,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"衝警署務必三思 可以好大罪<br />\n<br />\n諗清楚衝警署對事情幫忙是正面定負面<br />\n<br />\n衝警署同衝立會的社會印象完全是兩回事<br />\n<br />\n諗清楚要爭取D咩，訴求要清晰<br />\n<br />\n例如：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>警隊改革 獨立調查</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n爭取開明派 中間派市民支持<br />\n<br />\n如果可以觸動到再搞一兩次大遊行<br />\n<br />\n咁我地先贏<br />\n<br />\n千萬不要主動衝！"},{"pid":"1049b1f9543df882c06997faa882746294859bea","tid":1248133,"uid":36920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:13:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f254aa2299c96eabe33f6e0074cf37721b0706b2","tid":1248133,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:17:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f6d92011da6220c84289a7fa81abd99516e59a7c","tid":1248133,"uid":102343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:20:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"aea52ee644342e094bffc22c0a7e5f654800dca5","tid":1248133,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:21:01.000Z","msg":"三毛又出動"},{"pid":"fc1e88862752af6ae8b59a8e0d6934027984f0d6","tid":1248133,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:21:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5ffa334c65064b56664c7f6236a5d1c66e9a30d7","tid":1248133,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11:24:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家警方有49單999緊急服務延誤左<br />\n又打慘情牌想利用市民</span></span>"},{"pid":"4f2046c786d3ffdd3cf1b846788ee71ee41176cf","tid":1248133,"uid":137170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T11: